And did they like this new book?

00:11:57.170 --> 00:11:58.470
&gt;&gt; No.

00:11:58.470 --> 00:11:59.770
&gt;&gt; Yeah.

00:11:59.770 --> 00:12:01.070
&gt;&gt; No. They didn't [laughter].

00:12:01.070 --> 00:12:03.090
Thanks for that vote of
confidence down there, but no.

00:12:03.090 --> 00:12:08.110
Every publisher that saw
this book rejected the book.

00:12:08.110 --> 00:12:13.780
But in one moment of the story,
on one page of the book, the boy,

00:12:13.780 --> 00:12:17.570
