later inspire me

00:12:24.970 --> 00:12:27.100
to write that book Baghead.

00:12:27.100 --> 00:12:28.400
That would get published.

00:12:28.400 --> 00:12:30.800
This one scene would
later be expanded

00:12:30.800 --> 00:12:33.280
