00:13:28.660 --> 00:13:32.650
And how many of those 80
people got in touch with me?

00:13:32.650 --> 00:13:33.950
&gt;&gt; One.

00:13:33.950 --> 00:13:35.250
&gt;&gt; Well, one is a good
guess, but no.

00:13:35.250 --> 00:13:36.550
Fewer than that.

00:13:36.550 --> 00:13:37.850
Zero [laughter].

00:13:37.850 --> 00:13:39.390
Yeah. Nobody did.

00:13:39.390 --> 00:13:40.790
So I painted another picture.

00:13:40.790 --> 00:13:44.020
The next week I printed
up another 80 postcards.

00:13:44.020 --> 00:13:45.690
And how many people
got in touch with me?

00:13:45.690 --> 00:13:46.990
&gt;&gt; Zero.

00:13:46.990 --> 00:13:50.470
&gt;&gt; None. And so week after
week and month after month,

00:13:50.470 --> 00:13:55.250
