00:14:14.230 --> 00:14:15.530
About a boy.

00:14:15.530 --> 00:14:16.830
He wears monkey pajamas.

00:14:16.830 --> 00:14:18.130
He doesn't want to go to bed.

00:14:18.130 --> 00:14:20.540 position:56%
And then I painted this illustration

00:14:20.540 --> 00:14:23.550
and I put this illustration
on a postcard.

00:14:23.550 --> 00:14:25.710
I printed up 80 postcards.

00:14:25.710 --> 00:14:28.180
I mailed them out to 80
different people at all

00:14:28.180 --> 00:14:30.470
of these different publishers.

00:14:30.470 --> 00:14:34.160
And of the 80 people who
received these postcards,

00:14:34.160 --> 00:14:36.430
how many of those 80
people got in touch with me?

00:14:36.430 --> 00:14:38.590
&gt;&gt; Zero.

00:14:38.590 --> 00:14:41.550
