00:14:41.550 --> 00:14:46.430
I received an e-mail from an editor
at Random House Children's Books.

00:14:46.430 --> 00:14:47.940
And that's a big publisher.

00:14:47.940 --> 00:14:49.750
And I couldn't believe it.

00:14:49.750 --> 00:14:52.640
And to give you a perspective
