00:14:52.640 --> 00:14:53.940
From the time that I turned

00:14:53.940 --> 00:14:55.660
on my computer till I
could download the e-mail,

00:14:55.660 --> 00:14:57.430
it took me 20 minutes [laughter]

00:14:57.430 --> 00:14:59.710
because that's what life
was like in the late '90s.

00:14:59.710 --> 00:15:02.310
You had to connect to a phone line.

00:15:02.310 --> 00:15:04.430
There was an awful sound.

00:15:04.430 --> 00:15:08.430
But 20 minutes later, after turning
on the computer, I got this e-mail

00:15:08.430 --> 00:15:10.700
from somebody at Random House.

00:15:10.700 --> 00:15:12.840
And the subject of the
e-mail said nice work.

00:15:12.840 --> 00:15:14.880
And I couldn't believe it.

00:15:14.880 --> 00:15:17.080
And in this e-mail,
this editor wrote

00:15:17.080 --> 00:15:19.560
