New York City, please let me know.

00:15:26.340 --> 00:15:29.980
We'd love to meet you and
see some more of your work.

00:15:29.980 --> 00:15:32.300
So do you guys suppose that
I happened to be in New York

00:15:32.300 --> 00:15:33.600
