00:15:33.600 --> 00:15:36.790
&gt;&gt; Yeah. I called her the next
day to say I'm going to be

00:15:36.790 --> 00:15:38.090
in New York that next week.

00:15:38.090 --> 00:15:39.390
And we set up a meeting.

00:15:39.390 --> 00:15:41.380
And I went into New
York with my portfolio.

00:15:41.380 --> 00:15:43.400
And I showed this editor
all of my artwork,

00:15:43.400 --> 00:15:45.990
and I showed her all
of my book ideas.

00:15:45.990 --> 00:15:48.140
And I left New York
